(260, 1, '2018-05-01 21:38:51', '2018-05-01 16:08:51', 'The fifth edition of KIIT International Model United Nations aspired to acknowledge the importance the underprivileged indigenous masses of the world. Last October, with eighteen committees, a total participation of more than 1,800 Delegates as well as Press members from across the world, three days of extensive deliberations and networking events, the conference has morphed itself into one of the premiere Model United Nation simulations of the world.\r\n\r\nThe event was graced by eminent personalities such Mrs. Ashwiny Iyer Tiwari – the award winning Indian film-maker, Mr. Sergio Arispe Barrientos – the Bolivian Ambassador to India, Mr. Kamal Singh – the Executive Director of the UN Global Compact India, Mr. Punya Prasun Bajpai – the Executive Editor of <em>Aaj Tak</em>, as well as Mr. R. S. Prasanna – the director of ‘<em>Shubh Mangal Saavdhan’</em>. Words of wisdom and the august presence of such illustrious characters at the conference played a monumental role in inspiring the young delegates to take up the charge of discussing effective ways of incorporating positive changes in the society.\r\n\r\nExhilarating after-conference events and networking dinners have never been an option at KIIT International MUN, but rather, a tradition that has prevailed, and is here to stay. KIIT Intl. MUN 2017 was graced by Mr. Kenneth Sebastian, a famous Indian stand-up comedian, musician, and film-maker. From gags on his popular show, \'Chai time with Kenny\' to talking about \'Tinkle\'- our childhood companion or \'middle class restaurant problems\'; Kenny seemed to be well-versed with the art of tickling his audience\'s funny bones.\r\n\r\nThe very essence of our motive for organizing such an event lies in the involvement of the Youth in issues that demand global concern, in order to provide them with an intensive understanding of the ways in which the UN functions. In the last version of the conference, we perceived ourselves as a community of responsible stakeholders of the world who aim to tackle formidable subjects of contention by means of effective research and deliberations. Such a framework not only ensured awareness about the world at large, but also inculcated the notion that a unified and procedural approach towards a problem can play a decisive role in breaking through the stringency of any issue at hand.', 'About KIITMUN', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about-kiitmun', '', '', '2018-05-23 23:54:50', '2018-05-23 18:24:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost/KiitMun18/?p=260', 0, 'post', '', 0),
