(456, 1, '2018-05-27 17:03:46', '2018-05-27 11:33:46', 'The first committee in the United Nations, the Disarmament and International Security committee (DISEC), was established in 1946 and resides under the direct control of the General Assembly of the United Nations. The primary functions of the council are prevention of imminent conflicts, mediation and resolution for the persistent maintenance of international peace and security among nations.This committee is based on the \"One Member, One Vote Principle\", and includes representatives from all the 193 member nations of the UN.\r\n\r\n<strong>Committee level: Beginner</strong>\r\n<strong> Committee Strength: 160 (Double Delegate)</strong>', 'United Nations Disarmament and International Security Committee (DISEC)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '293-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-05-27 17:03:46', '2018-05-27 11:33:46', '', 293, 'http://localhost/KiitMun18/293-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
